<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drop-in">drop in</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>顺便走访：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please drop in any time you like. 
欢迎随时来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will you drop in on us tomorrow evening for a talk?
你明晚顺便来和我们谈谈好吗？</p></div>

<p>注: 顺便走访某人为“drop in on sb”；顺便走访 某地为“drop in at some place”。  </p></div>